trans-unit.source: Represents an ordered list of <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma lista ordenada de <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A TimerEventSubscriptionCollection represents the queue of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription> objects associated with a workflow instance and provides methods to manage this queue.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Um TimerEventSubscriptionCollection representa a fila de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription>objetos associados a um fluxo de trabalho de instância e fornece métodos para gerenciar essa fila.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription>

trans-unit.source: Subscriptions are ordered in the queue based on their <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> values; those with smaller <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> values are positioned before those with larger <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> values.
trans-unit.target: As assinaturas são classificadas na fila com base em seus <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>valores; aquelas com menor <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>valores são posicionados antes daqueles com maior <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>valores.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can use the methods provided by this class to manage the collection of active timer event subscriptions exposed by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty> for each workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Você pode usar os métodos fornecidos por esta classe para gerenciar a coleção de assinaturas de evento de temporizador ativo expostos pelo <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>para cada instância de fluxo de trabalho.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.TimerCollectionProperty>

trans-unit.source: You can use <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Add%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Remove%2A> to add or remove subscriptions from the timer queue.
trans-unit.target: Você pode usar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Add%2A>ou <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Remove%2A>para adicionar ou remover assinaturas da fila de timer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Remove%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscriptionCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: Whenever the first element in the timer queue changes, the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService> is called to cancel the timer event that was previously at the beginning of the queue and schedule the new timer event.
trans-unit.target: Sempre que o primeiro elemento na fila de timer for alterado, o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService>é chamado para cancelar o evento de timer que era anteriormente no início da fila e o novo evento de timer de agendamento.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService>

trans-unit.source: Adds the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription> to the timer queue.

trans-unit.source: Subscriptions in the queue are positioned based on their <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A?displayProperty=fullName> values; those with smaller values are positioned in front of those with larger values.
trans-unit.target: As assinaturas na fila são posicionadas com base nas suas <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A?displayProperty=fullName>valores; aquelas com valores menores são posicionadas na frente com valores maiores.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.TimerEventSubscription.ExpiresAt%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: If the new subscription is added at the beginning of the queue, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is called to cancel the timer event that was previously at the beginning of the queue and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Schedule%28System.Threading.WaitCallback%2CSystem.Guid%2CSystem.DateTime%2CSystem.Guid%29?displayProperty=fullName> is called to schedule the new timer event.
trans-unit.target: Se a nova assinatura é adicionada no início da fila, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName>é chamado para cancelar o evento de timer que era anteriormente no início da fila e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Schedule%28System.Threading.WaitCallback%2CSystem.Guid%2CSystem.DateTime%2CSystem.Guid%29?displayProperty=fullName>é chamado para agendar o novo evento de timer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Schedule%28System.Threading.WaitCallback%2CSystem.Guid%2CSystem.DateTime%2CSystem.Guid%29?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Hosting.WorkflowSchedulerService.Cancel%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
